snippet: Mrs. Clinton and her husband reported $10.6 million in adjusted gross income for 2015....
abstract: Hillary Clinton and Sen Tim Kaine release their 2015 tax returns, putting pressure on Donald Trump to make public his own tax returns, which he has so far declined to do.

byline.original: By STEVE EDER and KITTY BENNETT

lead_paragraph: Mrs. Clinton and her husband reported $10.6 million in adjusted gross income for 2015.

headline.main: Hillary Clinton and Tim Kaine Show New Tax Returns, Pressuring Donald Trump
headline.print_headline: Clinton and Kaine, Raising Ante, Release More Tax Returns
